Title: Transcarent To Acquire Part Of AI-Powered 98point6 In $100 Million Healthtech Deal
Description: As the AI race heats up in healthcare, 98point6 is selling its physician group and self-insured employer business to Transcarent and will pivot to selling its software to health systems.

Title: 2023 Layoff Tracker: Atlassian And SiriusXM Conduct Major Layoffs
Description: Amazon, Alphabet, Salesforce and Disney have all slashed staff this year, citing cloudy economic forecasts.
